Name: Maze Workout - Urban Lost Solo Car Racer
About the game: It's a car racing maze game with progressive difficulty levels, that starts from very easy to more complex. You are alone in the game. it's a single player game. But with the option to save multiple user profiles. The ambiance in the game is calm and relaxing, with a modern outdoor architecture style. As the name indicates you should play the levels many times to get better record times. It's a 52 level racing game to find the checkpoints and do the needed laps to the finish line. Good luck!
